Summer moon<br />
In your shade I&#8217;ll wander<br />
In the bewitched starlight<br />
Flowers will be kisses</p>
<p>I came standing near you<br />
Small ship on the seashore<br />
I tremble the shades of the night<br />
Therefore love me, my moon</p>
<p>Summer moon<br />
On the sky of love<br />
The bewitched starlight<br />
Flowers make kisses</p>
<p>Look at the desolate seashore<br />
I whisper you &#8220;I love you&#8221;<br />
Now I&#8217;ll build a church<br />
For the crazy children of love</p>
